name: FON Strike Scene Evidence
description: This data chip contains within it compelling evidence suggesting that the Wiyrkomi corporation has hired mercenaries to attack its own contracted mercenaries in an attempt to martyrize itself, thus subverting the Gallente public's opinion of their industrial operations in the Algintal system.  It should be taken to Preaux Gallot, FON activist at the Natura Seminary in Audaerne, right away.
